title: Wall Street Breakfast May 27: Mortgage Rates Continue to Fall on Headwinds Facing Economy
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Mortgage rates continue to fall on headwinds facing the economy. Biden climate formulas upheld for now by the Supreme Court. Nearly one in five home sellers lower price, the highest rate since October 2019. Catch today’s WSB article here.
